//! User-owned extensions for the types and client generated from
//! `specs/sabre-booking/spec.openapi.yaml`.
//!
//! Scaffolded once by openapi-codegen and never touched again: this file
//! carries no `// @generated` marker, so regeneration skips it and stale
//! cleanup ignores it — the same is true of anything you add under `ext/`
//! (`pub mod hooks;`, `pub mod pcc;`, …).
//!
//! This is the coherence-legal home for code that belongs next to the
//! generated output: `impl` blocks on generated types, helper types, and
//! body hooks to register via `client::ClientBuilder::body_hook`.
